---
source: crates/daemon/tests/cli_help.rs
expression: stdout
---
List or inspect background jobs (large batch mutations, progress, undo ids)

Usage: mxr jobs [OPTIONS] [JOB_ID]

Arguments:
  [JOB_ID]  Optional job id to inspect. Omit to list recent jobs

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
